        "subject": "LU-472 Revive replay-single 61d",
        "message": "LU-472 Revive replay-single 61d\n\nOver the years, replay-single 61d had been forgotten in ALWAYS_EXCEPT,\nwith its fault injection changed to a location where an error could\nnever happen.  This patch fixes the subtest and removes it from\nALWAYS_EXCEPT.  See LU-472 for the full story.\n\nChange-Id: I1bf7d4c4178bd47d165f01b96567cc087ebdf644\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <liwei@whamcloud.com>\n"
